{"tid":2250938,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 13設計大爆料 瀏海變小Touch ID回歸","createTime":"2020-10-20T12:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T04:58:38.000Z","uid":221827,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d0a06731d1343ed3f2f5418a895d733d4e22f285","tid":2250938,"uid":221827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"蘋果iPhone 12系列機種將在10月23日開賣，但外媒關注的蘋果爆料達人已經先透露蘋果下一代新機（暫稱iPhone 13）的消息，指出iPhone 13的設計和螢幕將是許多果粉期望的改變：瀏海變小，重新引進Touch ID指紋辨識功能等。<br />\n<br />\n富比士（Forbes）網站專欄作家凱利（Gordon Kelly）統整知名爆料達人普瑟澤（Jon Prosser）、冰宇宙（Ice Universe）、楊恩（Ross Young）等人透露的iPhone 13訊息。<br />\n<br />\n普瑟澤和冰宇宙認同在蘋果會在iPhone 13縮減瀏海尺寸，但普瑟澤說，瀏海區域是橫向變窄，冰宇宙則說是直向變短；可能是因蘋果開發階段有多種原型機的緣故。<br />\n<br />\n此外，螢幕專家楊恩透露，除了臉部辨識之外，蘋果會重新引進Touch ID指紋辨識功能，以因應新冠肺炎疫情期間人們戴口罩的需求，相機感測器也將比iPhone 12更大，採用LTPO（低溫多晶氧化物）顯示面板。<br />\n<br />\nLTPO很省電，iPhone 12系列的螢幕原本想搭載120Hz自動適應更新率技術（ProMotion），但三星今年將庫存保留給自家的Note 20 Ultra手機，蘋果只得取消ProMotion，iPhone 13會修正這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://udn.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fudn.com&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEfroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=5b507b82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">udn.com</a>"},{"pid":"6de16865a2aab1558ca95c5775217741e9a8ee12","tid":2250938,"uid":25619,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:33:16.000Z","msg":"又撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07100288355fa0345b450240d13410da58a88f2b","tid":2250938,"uid":276153,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"應該買ip12定係等ip13好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912b52896df28c7be53005173eb827c18ff72feb","tid":2250938,"uid":20890,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:38:08.000Z","msg":"我由7plus俾人撚到12了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1beb2ac96b